Kernel module to demonstrate ioctl useage in Kernel space and User space

do a make ro build the module

sudo ./user_ioctl.out    - fetch the initial values
sudo ./user_ioctl.out -g - get the values from kernel
sudo ./user_ioctl.out -s - set the values for modules
sudo ./user_ioctl.out -c - clear the values and set it to 0
